                     Documentation for Global Arrays

You will find here:

Supercomputing94.ps.Z 	original SC'94 paper describing GA
UserGuide.html		preliminary User Guide in HTML
ga.ops.html		documentation for all GA operations in HTML
global.doc		documentation in ASCII
ga.index.html		alphabetical reference index of for the GA operations 
                        with links to the documentation (GA programmers make 
                        bookmark in their browsers to this file)

More information is available through links in the GA homepage:
http://www.emsl.pnl.gov:2080/docs/global/ga.html.
